  <brief_title>A Registry-based Cluster Randomized Trial to Compare the Effect of Spironolactone vs. Eplerenone on Clinical Outcomes in Patients With Symptomatic Systolic Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <acronym>CROWD-ASPECT</acronym>
  <official_title>Cluster and Registry Trials Of the Working Group of Heart Failure in Denmark: Are SPironolactone and Eplerenone Comparable Treatments?</official_title>
